textAfterTable: Description Best Videos of the Day - youtube Edition is a universal iOS app that delivers the most talked about and most watched videos of the day. Why search endlessly for the videos your friends are talking about when we can bring them right to your phone each day! Be the first to see hot new music videos, movie trailers, news clips, funny videos and more. You can easily save and share your favorite videos, go back in time to see the best videos of previous days, and access the entire youtube library to find even more great videos.
